: "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "outer covering,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZihaArap", "text_ar": "ظِهَارَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of a bed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, Mgh, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon which one sleeps,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of a thing that is spread upon the ground to sit"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "lie upon,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "whatever it be:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a sort of carpet"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "other thing that is spread upon the ground:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a woollen cloth"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, Msb, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "which is thrown over the"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "kind of vehicle called"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "hawodaj", "text_ar": "هَوْدَج"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Mgh, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "having a fine nap,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pile,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of some colour; what is white being seldom"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "never so called:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a sort of dyed cloth, like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zawojN", "text_ar": "زَوْجٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "these names being seldom"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "never applied but to what is coloured red"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "green"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "yellow; what is white not being called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "namaTN", "text_ar": "نَمَطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Az, L:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a cloth that is spread beneath a horse's saddle:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Meyd, as cited by Golius:) some say, that it is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a receptacle like the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "safaT", "text_ar": "سَفَط"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Har, p."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "273", "text_ar": ""}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[but this I think doubtful:] pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^anomaATN", "text_ar": "اَنْمَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[properly a pl. of pauc. but used also as one of mult.] (S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nimaATN", "text_ar": "نِمَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (IB, K.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A body of men"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh, Msb, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "whose case is one;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a class of men."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K.) It is said in a trad., (S, Mgh,) of 'Alee, (Mgh,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xayoru h`*ihi AlA^um~api Aln~amaTu AlA^awosaTu", "text_ar": "خَيْرُ هٰذِهِ الاُمَّةِ النَّمَطُ الاَوْسَطُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The best of this people is the middle body thereof"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "whose case is one;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the middle class thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, in which is added,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yuloHaqu bihimu Alt~aAliY wayurojaEu A_ilayohimu", "text_ar": "يُلْحَقُ بِهِمُ التَّالِى وَيُرْجَعُ اـِلَيْهِمُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlgaAliY", "text_ar": "الغَالِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he who falls short shall be made to reach them, and he who exceeds the due bounds shall be brought back to them:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]) A 'Obeyd says, (Mgh, TA,) the meaning of this saying of 'Alee is, (TA,) that he disliked the exceeding of the due bounds and the falling short (Mgh, TA) in religion. (TA.)       -A3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A way:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a way, course, mode,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "manner, of acting, conduct,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the like;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, K;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AnmT", "text_ar": "انمط", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA [so there written, without any syll. points:])"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a tenet,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "body of tenets, belief, creed, opinion,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "persuasion, which one takes to,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "holds:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a kind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "way, of speech."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ilozamo h`*aA Aln~maTa", "text_ar": "اـِلْزَمْ هٰذَا النّمَطَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "keep thou to this way."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "takal~amuwA EalaY namaTK waAHidK", "text_ar": "تَكَلَّمُوا عَلَى نَمَطٍ وَاحِدٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They spoke according to one way, course, mode,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "manner,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A sort,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "species,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, Msb, K,) of a thing, (K,) of goods or commodities, of learning or. science, &c. (TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EinodiY mataAEN mino h`*aA Aln~amaTi", "text_ar": "عِنْدِى مَتَاعٌ مِنْ هٰذَا النَّمَطِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I have goods of this sort,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "species."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*aA mino namaTi h`*aA", "text_ar": "هٰذَا مِنْ نَمَطِ هٰذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This is of the sort,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "species, of this."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.)"}], "source_refs": ["T", "Mgh", "K", "S", "Msb", "TA", "Az", "L"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}